ChatGPT Can Write Music
text:
You can simply ask:

"Can you write a song using ABC Notation? I want it in the style of Mozart."

and get an answer like:

============ Certainly! Here's a simple tune in the style of Mozart that you can play on any instrument or sing along to:

X:1

T: Mozartian Melody

C: ChatGPT

M:4/4

L:1/8

Q:1/4=120

K:C

G3 G B3 B | c3 c d3 d |

e3 e c3 c | d3 d B,3 B, |

c3 c A3 A | G3 G F3 F |

E3 E D3 D | C6 ||

G3 G B3 B | c3 c d3 d |

e3 e c3 c | d3 d B,3 B, |

c3 c A3 A | G3 G F3 F |

E3 E D3 D | C6 ||

G3 G B3 B | c3 c d3 d |

e3 e c3 c | d3 d B,3 B, |

c3 c A3 A | G3 G F3 F |

E3 E D3 D | C6 ||

G3 G B3 B | c3 c d3 d |

e3 e c3 c | d3 d B,3 B, |

c3 c A3 A | G3 G F3 F |

E3 E D3 D | C6 ||

Just copy and paste this code into an ABC notation editor or a music notation software that supports ABC notation, and you'll be able to hear or read the tune. Note that this is just a simple tune in the style of Mozart, and it's up to you to add your own embellishments and variations to make it your own. Enjoy!

============

Than you can copy/paste and play it in website like https://abc.rectanglered.com/ (you have to remove empty lines if you want to copy/paste from above).
